---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = 'July 11, 2026';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy — Pianeta.Studio" description="Privacy notice pursuant to Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (GDPR)." chrome={true}>
  <article class="detail-page">
    <header class="detail-head">
      <p class="detail-eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="detail-title">Privacy Notice</h1>
      <p class="detail-deck">Pursuant to Articles 13-14 of Regulation (EU) 2016/679 — GDPR.</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;opacity:0.7;margin-top:8px">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </header>

    <div class="detail-body prose-eclag">
      <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>PIANETA.STUDIO S.R.L. S.B.</strong> (single-shareholder Benefit Corporation) —
        Via IV Novembre 18, 95037 San Giovanni La Punta (CT), Italy — VAT/Tax ID 06037730873 — REA CT-459996.<br/>
        PEC: <a href="mailto:pianeta.studiosrlsb@legalmail.it">pianeta.studiosrlsb@legalmail.it</a> —
        email: <a href="mailto:max@pianeta.studio">max@pianeta.studio</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Data collected and purposes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contact via form / email</strong> (name, email, company, message) — replying to requests. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(b) pre-contractual measures; retention 24 months from last contact.</li>
        <li><strong>Commercial requests via /hire</strong> (intake fields plus any conversation with the Alba assistant) — lead qualification, proposal, contracting. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(b); retention 24 months or duration of the contract.</li>
        <li><strong>Newsletter signup (Bulletin, announcements)</strong> — sending editorial content and studio updates. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(a) consent; retention until consent is withdrawn.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical and analytics cookies</strong> — site operation and anonymous traffic measurement. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) legitimate interest for technical cookies; Art. 6(1)(a) consent for analytics and marketing. Details in <a href="/en/cookie">Cookie Policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Accounting and tax obligations</strong> (invoicing, contracts) — statutory duties. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(c); retention 10 years.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Recipients and processors</h2>
      <p>Data is processed with third-party tools appointed as Processors under Art. 28 GDPR:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Vercel Inc.</strong> — website hosting (USA)</li>
        <li><strong>Supabase Inc.</strong> — application database (EU/USA)</li>
        <li><strong>Resend</strong> — transactional and newsletter email (USA)</li>
        <li><strong>Stripe Payments Europe</strong> — /hire payments (Ireland / USA)</li>
        <li><strong>Google LLC</strong> — Google Analytics 4, Google Ads (USA)</li>
        <li><strong>Anthropic PBC</strong> — LLM powering the Alba assistant (USA)</li>
        <li><strong>Etastudio</strong> — tax/accounting advisor (Italy)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. International transfers</h2>
      <p>Transfers to US providers (Vercel, Stripe, Resend, Google, Anthropic) rely on Standard Contractual Clauses approved by the European Commission (Decision 2021/914) and, where applicable, participation in the <em>EU-US Data Privacy Framework</em>.</p>

      <h2>5. Data subject rights</h2>
      <p>Under Articles 15-22 GDPR you may exercise access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, objection and consent-withdrawal rights at any time by writing to <a href="mailto:max@pianeta.studio">max@pianeta.studio</a>. You may also lodge a complaint with the Italian Data Protection Authority (<a href="https://www.garanteprivacy.it" target="_blank" rel="noopener">garanteprivacy.it</a>).</p>

      <h2>6. Processing and security</h2>
      <p>Processing is carried out electronically with TLS in-transit encryption, access controls and regular backups. No automated decision-making producing legal effects on the data subject under Art. 22 GDPR is performed.</p>

      <h2>7. Updates</h2>
      <p>This notice may be updated to reflect regulatory or operational changes. The current version is always published at this URL. Last-updated date shown at the top of this page.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
